timing_enable...al_derate_mode(25.10)    timing_enable...al_derate_mode(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_spatial_derate_mode

Syntax
       timing_enable_spatial_derate_mode

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables the spatial derate mode.

       When  set  to true, the software allows access to the GBA spatial modes
       (bounding_box or  chip_size)  specified  with  the  timing_spatial_der-
       ate_distance_mode global variable.

       When  set  to false, the software allows you to specify only the bound-
       ing_box option.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

